long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tabdash is the ultimate tab search extension that empowers you to effortlessly find and organize your tabs. With its intuitive interface and lightning-fast search capabilities, Tabdash simplifies your browsing experience, allowing you to effortlessly navigate through your open tabs. Take control of your browsing journey with Tabdash and unlock a new level of efficiency and productivity.

Shortcuts to activate Tabdash:

* CTRL+E/CMD+E(on Macs)
* CTRL+SPACE/ALT+SPACE(on Macs)
